{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-articles-articles-template-js","path":"/articles/iterm2/iterm-setup.html","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Happy coding life","author":"@yolokuder"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"f435fdc5-a4cb-5d54-bc26-283ec2ffb18b","excerpt":"How to install iTerm2 You would Download iTerm2 and install it. Then getting the iTerm color settings. My favorite color them is Solarized Dark theme Just save…","html":"<h1 id=\"how-to-install-iterm2\"><a href=\"#how-to-install-iterm2\" aria-label=\"how to install iterm2 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to install iTerm2</h1>\n<p>You would <a href=\"http://www.iterm2.com/downloads.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Download iTerm2</a> and install it.</p>\n<p>Then getting the iTerm color settings. My favorite color them is <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mbadolato/iTerm2-Color-Schemes/master/schemes/Solarized%20Dark%20-%20Patched.itermcolors\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Solarized Dark theme</a></p>\n<p>Just save it somewhere and open the file(s). The color settings will be imported into iTerm2. Apply them in iTerm through iTerm → preferences → profiles → colors → load presets.</p>\n<h1 id=\"oh-my-zsh\"><a href=\"#oh-my-zsh\" aria-label=\"oh my zsh permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Oh My Zsh</h1>\n<p>First step is installing with curl</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"gatsby-code-shell\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">sh</span> -c <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">curl</span> -fsSL https://raw.github.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh/master/tools/install.sh<span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>I like to see some added info so I install <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">Powerlevel9k</code>. Just execute</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"gatsby-code-shell\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">git</span> clone https://github.com/bhilburn/powerlevel9k.git ~/.oh-my-zsh/custom/themes/powerlevel9k</code></pre></div>\n<p>When the installation is done, edit <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">~/.zshrc</code> and set <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">ZSH_THEME=&quot;powerlevel9k/powerlevel9k&quot;</code></p>\n<p>Here is my final <a href=\"/2a95d44665c842f3e279c9f16bca8453/.zshrc.\">.zshrc file</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"install-a-patched-font\"><a href=\"#install-a-patched-font\" aria-label=\"install a patched font permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install a patched font</h2>\n<p>I use <a href=\"https://github.com/powerline/fonts/blob/master/Meslo%20Slashed/Meslo%20LG%20M%20Regular%20for%20Powerline.ttf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Meslo</a> font for iTerm2. Click “view raw” to download the font.</p>\n<p>Open the downloaded font and press “Install Font”.</p>\n<p>Set this font in iTerm2 (14px is my personal preference) (iTerm → Preferences → Profiles → Text → Change Font).</p>\n<p>Restart iTerm2 for all changes to take effect.</p>\n<h1 id=\"further-tweaking\"><a href=\"#further-tweaking\" aria-label=\"further tweaking permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Further tweaking</h1>\n<p>I make some tweak to show nice prompt by adding these setting to <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">.zshrc</code> file</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"gatsby-code-text\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">POWERLEVEL9K_SHORTEN_DIR_LENGTH=1\nPOWERLEVEL9K_CONTEXT_TEMPLATE=&quot;\\u2665 YolokKuder.com \\u2665&quot;\nPOWERLEVEL9K_LEFT_PROMPT_ELEMENTS=(context dir vcs)\nPOWERLEVEL9K_SHORTEN_DELIMITER=&quot;..&quot;</code></pre></div>\n<p>Here is my final <a href=\"/2a95d44665c842f3e279c9f16bca8453/.zshrc.\">.zshrc file</a></p>\n<p>That’s it, now just launch iterm and enjoy what we got.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"iterm2 setup","date":"July 07, 2019","description":"Setup iterm2 on MAC."}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/articles/iterm2/iterm-setup.html"}}}